1
00:00:27,219 --> 00:00:30,480
무너진 도시의 잔해 위로
Over the ruins of a collapsed city

2
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:33,219
붉은 신호등이 깜빡여
A red traffic light blinks

3
00:00:33,979 --> 00:00:37,039
